1. Using your card
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
You can use your card both
in Denmark and abroad. You may not use the card for unlawful
purposes, including the purchase of goods or services that are
illegal according to local legislation.
.sp 3mm
MasterCard on mobile can be used when making physical purchases from
payment recipients accepting contactless cards.
