1.6. Withdrawal of sums from your account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
In principle, purchases and cash withdrawals will be debited from your
account on the same day that you make the purchase or withdrawal. The time
of debiting from your account will, however, depend on when &BANKNAVN.
receives the transaction.
