1.8. Issuing cards and setting up card accounts
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Cards are issued on the basis of individual credit assessment of the
applicant, see Article 4.
Cards can only be issued to persons of at least 18 years of age who are
not under orders of guardianship.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Cards are normally issued for three years at a time. The month and year
of expiry are stamped into the card. The card will be sent to you by
standard mail at the address that &BANKNAVN. has listed for you.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
It is a precondition that payment be registered with Betalingsservice
or a fixed transfer arrangement in &BANKNAVN. - regardless of card type.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
On issuing your card, &BANKNAVN. will also set up a card account for
you. Every time you use the card, the sum will subsequently be
registered on this card account. The consolidated sum and any interest
and charges applicable to same will be invoiced to you once a month.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Corporate cards with corporate liability
:SKRSLUT.
.br
On setting up Corporate cards with corporate liability, &BANKNAVN. will
assess the company's financial position, see Article 4. The consumption
limit on the card is the maximum sum at your disposal on your card
account.
